[19:53:26.423] [Info] Chat: <???> Have a very safe and educational day.
[19:53:37.116] [Info] Chat: <???> It is imperative to note that due to the nature of the tests in this facility, you may very well end up stuck through very much fault of your own.
[19:53:49.796] [Info] Chat: <???> If this happens, please feel free to assume a fetal position, weep at your lack of forethought, and beam out of the facility.
